desc: Coaching adults through the college application process now when you are more focused and dedicated then ever. Let me teach you the business side of college in order to help you create a plan and road map for college success to enhance your career, before you spend thousands of dollars in financial aid.

layout.text: Knowing your purpose and creating a plan to attend college is more important than ever. Join us while we help you plan for college the SMART Way. ARE YOU READY?
